  <TITLE>Add &quot;Shipping by Total&quot; functionality to &quot;Shipping by Weight&quot; plugin</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>It is only needed to add the &quot;Order subtotal From&quot; and &quot;Order subtotal to&quot; columns (defaults: 0 and 1000000 respectively) to the Shipping by Weight plugin and it will cover both cases weight and total. Then rename existing &quot;From&quot; and &quot;To&quot; properties to &quot;Weight from&quot; and &quot;Weight to&quot; respectively. We alread have &quot;fixed&quot; fee supported (use AdditionalFixedCost property). Now we just have to add appropriate filtering to &quot;FindRecord&quot; method of \Nop.Plugin.Shipping.FixedOrByWeight\Services\ShippingByWeightService.cs And of course, now we have to rename the plugin, appropriate database table, etc to soemthing else. Ideas? FixedWeightTotal? ShippingByWeightTotalRecord? Let's decide Source: http://www.nopcommerce.com/boards/t/45416/suggestion-combine-shipping-by-weight-and-shipping-by-total-shipping-providers.aspx At the same moment we already have a plugin (http://www.nopcommerce.com/p/669/shipping-by-total.aspx). Should we do it?</DESCRIPTION>
